sectionHeading: Regular traffic reports will resume Wednesday November 30 at 4:00 p.m.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for W Main St at Upper St
location: W Main St down to one lane due to an injury collision.  One vehicle hit a building.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for W Main St at Upper St
location: Access to S Upper St shutdown.  All traffic from N Upper St diverted to Main St.

incidentType: Traffic Advisory for W Main St at Upper St
